*******************************************************************************
* Walk Visualisation                                                        
*******************************************************************************

	A C++ application based on Qt 4 and CGAL to visualise and compare walks on
	triangulations.

*******************************************************************************
* About
*******************************************************************************

	Written by:             Ross Hemsley
	E-mail:                 ross.hemsley (at) inria.fr
	Blog of current work:   http://rosshemsley.co.uk

*******************************************************************************
* Compiling
*******************************************************************************

	This program requires Qt4, CGAL and cmake.

	$ cmake .
	$ make


